@antonimaciej I am happy to merge this but can we update the name of `format_` for all GCP Translate operators.

Can be changed to `format_text`? Ending the name with `_` is not something we should do, also Sphinx doesn't seem to render the name properly and seems to remove `_`. Example: https://airflow.readthedocs.io/en/latest/_api/airflow/contrib/operators/gcp_translate_operator/index.html#airflow.contrib.operators.gcp_translate_operator.CloudTranslateTextOperator

cc @potiuk
